NAME
     help - Get help on a command or topic

SYNOPSIS
     help <topic|command>

DESCRIPTION
     The help command provides help on commands and topics of discuss. 
     A complete list of commands can be obtained by using the 
     list_requests command (which can be abbreviated to just "?").
     Other topics available include:

	access - Help on access control lists for discuss meetings.
	specifiers, spec - Help on specifying transactions to commands.

SEE ALSO
     discuss(1)

DIAGNOSTICS
     discuss(help): No info found for [topic]
	There is no entry in the info directory for this topic.

BUGS
     There should be some way to list help topics.
